name: .DUMP File Extension
summary: Learn about .DUMP files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Crash log generated by Google BreakPad, a crash reporting tool used by Mozilla Firefox and other programs; may be saved by the program to the user's local file system when the program crashes, along with .EXTRA files.

content: DUMP files can be submitted with EXTRA files to the software developer so that the cause of the crash can be determined.
NOTE: DUMP files generated by Mozilla Firefox are saved to the [user]\​AppData\​Roaming\​Mozilla\​Firefox\​Crash Reports\​pending\​ directory.
